### Test Protected Endpoint (cần authentication)
### Thay YOUR_JWT_TOKEN bằng token nhận được từ login
GET https://localhost:7138/api/test/protected
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

###

### Test Admin Only Endpoint
### Chỉ ADMIN mới truy cập được
GET https://localhost:7138/api/test/admin-only
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

###

### Test Staff Only Endpoint
### EMPLOYEE và ADMIN có thể truy cập
GET https://localhost:7138/api/test/staff-only
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

